WEBVTT

00:00:06.599 --> 00:00:08.543
What is bipolar disorder?

00:00:08.543 --> 00:00:12.605
The word bipolar means two extremes.

00:00:12.605 --> 00:00:16.785
For the many millions experiencing
bipolar disorder around the world,

00:00:16.785 --> 00:00:20.405
life is split between 
two different realities -

00:00:20.405 --> 00:00:22.836
elation and depression.

00:00:22.836 --> 00:00:25.874
Although there are many variations
of bipolar disorder,

00:00:25.874 --> 00:00:27.816
let's consider a couple.

00:00:27.816 --> 00:00:31.915
